  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Romania Prop Hunt</strong></u> is a multiplayer game where you play with your friends and hide as a prop, an object from the game, and the Hunter tires to find them!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349600/extras/fb3e91cf78b94bad8d80b96b7822b46f.avif?t=1733344233\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349600/extras_big/fb3e91cf78b94bad8d80b96b7822b46f.avif?t=1733344233 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>PLAYSTYLE</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1 Hunter and a max of 7 hiders. Try to find other hidden players as props to win, if you get found you have to play as a Hunter to help find the others. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>FEATURES</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and fun gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a server online or LAN and play with your friends. MINIMUM OF 2 PLAYERS</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the beautiful maps from Romania.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>GENERAL MATURE CONTENT</strong></u></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The game may contain Explicit Words.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349600/extras/da93f77608f3ededd844f2e1f480c1c8.avif?t=1733344233\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349600/extras_big/da93f77608f3ededd844f2e1f480c1c8.avif?t=1733344233 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Romania Prop Hunt</strong></u> is a multiplayer game where you play with your friends and hide as a prop, an object from the game, and the Hunter tires to find them!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349600/extras/fb3e91cf78b94bad8d80b96b7822b46f.avif?t=1733344233\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349600/extras_big/fb3e91cf78b94bad8d80b96b7822b46f.avif?t=1733344233 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>PLAYSTYLE</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1 Hunter and a max of 7 hiders. Try to find other hidden players as props to win, if you get found you have to play as a Hunter to help find the others. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>FEATURES</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and fun gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a server online or LAN and play with your friends. MINIMUM OF 2 PLAYERS</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the beautiful maps from Romania.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>GENERAL MATURE CONTENT</strong></u></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The game may contain Explicit Words.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349600/extras/da93f77608f3ededd844f2e1f480c1c8.avif?t=1733344233\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349600/extras_big/da93f77608f3ededd844f2e1f480c1c8.avif?t=1733344233 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
